{"tid":813780,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳 慧 琳 三 點 式 泳 衣 照 微 博 流 傳","createTime":"2018-09-10T17:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T01:01:13.000Z","uid":24160,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"547ef9f4ff3b350b9af794cf7b29ca5ccbc6efa9","tid":813780,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:01:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.wenweipo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.wenweipo.com&d=oJvLZC8ezx0FqvPelps3GttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ccc62a4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.wenweipo.com</a>   [2010-05-25]   <br />\n<br />\n【文匯網訊】近日香港一班年輕模特趁夏日狂秀「事業線」，陳慧琳雖不年輕，但也絕不比嫩模們遜色，也以三點式上陣，風采猶存。<br />\n　近日陳慧琳的兩張昔日纖體廣告泳照在微博上廣泛流傳，陳慧琳的超低V泳裝及秀背靚照。來源：武漢晚報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2010/05/25/20100525gcx0027.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2010%2F05%2F25%2F20100525gcx0027.jpg&h=f9dde71d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be1d55085fe9e0797f5d3074922b812224c9fe47","tid":813780,"uid":193740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"替身？"},{"pid":"e264518db575a6def23545a4312d9841715733b1","tid":813780,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06ab4d2622e046cc3c249bb65a8e301ca356df72","tid":813780,"uid":203365,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"個樣點睇都似汪丫姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10849c7e0f6a375cd2fbfcb62f1d9dcca0ce6afb","tid":813780,"uid":7125,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"你都係攪番汪阿姐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c216e5a08f1b051ad0b1238b9bcc3a8f5daece57","tid":813780,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.pn